Webex App | Send a text message
If you need to send a text to somebody, write your message in the app and send it to their mobile number. You can also receive text messages in the app.
This feature is currently only available in the US and Canada for Webex Calling with Cisco Calling Plans.
Desktop
iOS
Android
1
In the app header, click , and choose Send a text message.
2
Enter +1 followed by the 10 digit number and click Create.
3
Enter your message and click to send.